TRANSFORMERS fans will get the chance to meet Optimus Prime as he visits St Enoch Centre. Prime time as Optimus visits mall TRANSFORMERS fans will get the chance to meet Optimus Prime as he visits St Enoch Centre.The leader of the Autobots will be appearing in both his truck and his transformed states from 11am to 4pm today.And there will be a full scale replica truck outside the centre's Tesco Express.Anne Ledgerwood, general manager of St Enoch Centre, said: &quot;We prides ourselves on staging fantastic events for all the family, even robots.&quot; 